# introduction

the [rust](https://www.rust-lang.org/)/[leptos](https://leptos.dev/) canarias course will feature a 'hands on' introduction to the rust programming language with modern AI workflows. 

* the morning is for rust
* the afternoon for leptos

# date + time + location

* 23 jan 2025 
* 16:30-20:00 o'clock, 20:00 is pizza break
* [at kreitek hacker space](https://kreitek.org/)

