# requirements

* `MUST`: bring a laptop
* `MUST`: create a <https://replit.com/> account and fire up your first repl with rust and evaluate hello world
* `MUST`: create a <https://chatgpt.com/> account and check it works by making a hello world query
* `MUST`: become familiar with <https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&mode=debug&edition=2021>
* `MUST`: read chapter 1 + 2 from <https://tourofrust.com/>
* you have **some experience with programming in general, no prior rust knowledge required** for this course
* course is in english

## optional

for more insights, finish this course <https://tourofrust.com/> before this workshop

